sourcesContent: async function e({accessToken:e,entropyId:r,entropyIdVerifier:a,transactingWallet:n,walletProxy:s,transactionRequest:i,publicClient:o,requesterAppId:c}){let p=await t({accessToken:e,entropyId:r,entropyIdVerifier:a,transactingWallet:n,walletProxy:s,transactionRequest:i,requesterAppId:c});return await o.sendRawTransaction({serializedTransaction:p})}async function t({accessToken:e,entropyId:t,entropyIdVerifier:r,transactingWallet:a,walletProxy:n,transactionRequest:s,requesterAppId:i}){return(await n.rpc({entropyId:t,entropyIdVerifier:r,hdWalletIndex:a.walletIndex??0,chainType:"ethereum",accessToken:e,requesterAppId:i,request:{method:"eth_signTransaction",params:[s]}})).response.data}export{e as sendTransaction,t as signTransaction};
